headline: How Cadence Bank, Kimberly-Clark, And Robert Half Can Put Cash In Your Pocket
summary: Companies with a long history of paying dividends and consistently hiking them remain appealing to income-focused investors. Cadence Bank, Kimberly-Clark, and Robert Half have rewarded shareholders for years and recently announced dividend increases. ...
